  <data name="ServiceTerminalSupportConsoleExampleHelp" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>All command help

{0} &lt;Command&gt;?

Command parameter help

Below are some examples of commands

1. Specify the necessary parameters
For example: help name
Take name as a parameter for the help command

2. Use "&amp;" to separate commands
For example: help &amp; help
Execute the "help" command twice in sequence

3. Use "-" to specify options
For example: help -{0} name
Use name as the {0} parameter for the help command

4. Use """ to concatenate content
For example: help "help name"
Treat "help name" as part of the same section

5. Use "\" to escape symbols
For example: help "wrap\nline"
Escape n as a newline character</value>
